                        THOMAS ROACH
                  . (Policeman, F 38). I produce a certificate—(Read: "Middlesex Sessions, July, 1854; Mary Williams, Convicted of stealing a watch from the person; 
Confined twelve months")—I was present—Mills is the person.





                        JOSIAH KING
                  . (Policeman). I produce a certificate of Moore's conviction—(Read: George Mowatt, Convicted at Westminster Sessions, Feb., 1856, of larceny from the person; 
Confined twelve months)—Moore is the person—I was present at the trial.

